00:00:16.370 --> 00:00:17.750
Hey!

00:00:17.750 --> 00:00:20.740
Good morning!

00:00:52.580 --> 00:00:54.690
If I can be like the idol, Miki-chan,

00:00:56.230 --> 00:00:58.500
and be just as cool and successful

00:00:59.710 --> 00:01:00.850
when I

00:01:01.580 --> 00:01:03.400
start at my new school...

00:01:07.690 --> 00:01:09.500
I can make lots...

00:01:09.500 --> 00:01:10.580
and lots...

00:01:10.750 --> 00:01:12.440
and lots...

00:01:17.060 --> 00:01:18.270
of friends!

00:01:20.260 --> 00:01:21.580
Yes!

00:01:21.580 --> 00:01:22.730
I did it!

00:01:27.370 --> 00:01:30.260
Wow, this water's cold.

00:01:30.260 --> 00:01:32.630
I wondered who I just saw fall down there.

00:01:34.240 --> 00:01:35.810
Hi, Taira-san!

00:01:35.810 --> 00:01:37.080
Should've known it was you, Komichi.

00:01:37.380 --> 00:01:39.610
Oh, I was just, uh...

00:01:39.610 --> 00:01:42.210
practicing swimming while fully clothed.

00:01:43.320 --> 00:01:46.150
I'll give you a lift home. Hop in the back.

00:01:48.740 --> 00:01:51.610
I hear you got into the middle
school you tested for.

00:01:51.610 --> 00:01:53.550
Yeah, Roubai Academy.

00:01:53.550 --> 00:01:55.600
It's a private school!

00:01:55.600 --> 00:01:59.360
I heard it's a tough school.
Didn't your mother go there?

00:01:59.360 --> 00:02:03.080
Yeah. That's why I'm so happy I got in!

00:02:03.080 --> 00:02:04.820
Are you, now?

00:02:04.820 --> 00:02:08.280
They say each class has more
than ten students in it!

00:02:08.280 --> 00:02:10.420
I can't even imagine it!

00:02:10.820 --> 00:02:12.700
Well, you were always the
only kid in your class

00:02:12.700 --> 00:02:14.900
back at Futaba Elementary.

00:02:15.570 --> 00:02:16.940
Good for you!

00:02:18.880 --> 00:02:19.740
Yeah!

00:02:21.070 --> 00:02:26.000
Akebi's Sailor Uniform

00:02:26.420 --> 00:02:28.380
Thank you!

