Roubai
\hAcademy

00:17:19.400 --> 00:17:23.980
I think... I got... a little too fired up.

00:17:26.870 --> 00:17:30.590
It's so big! It looks like a castle!

00:17:40.950 --> 00:17:42.460
Am I the first one here?

