00:17:48.150 --> 00:17:49.290
Class 3...

00:17:56.850 --> 00:17:57.990
Here it is.

00:18:00.550 --> 00:18:02.420
Someone's already here?!

00:18:02.420 --> 00:18:05.840
What if she's really scary?!

00:18:06.180 --> 00:18:08.350
Wow, what a weird outfit!

00:18:08.350 --> 00:18:10.840
I-It's not weird!

00:18:11.530 --> 00:18:13.740
We should try to get along!

00:18:13.740 --> 00:18:14.490
Osu!

00:18:15.400 --> 00:18:18.530
Why am I trying to fight them?!

00:18:45.870 --> 00:18:46.770
Um...

00:18:47.270 --> 00:18:49.050
Good morning.

00:18:49.470 --> 00:18:52.540
Good... morning...

00:18:56.310 --> 00:18:58.330
Please forget you ever saw that!

00:18:58.570 --> 00:18:59.320
Huh?

00:19:00.920 --> 00:19:03.020
I mean... you saw me, didn't you?

00:19:03.020 --> 00:19:06.030
When I was smelling my own
feet on the nail clippers.

00:19:06.320 --> 00:19:08.400
That's what she was doing?

00:19:08.760 --> 00:19:10.830
Sure. I won't tell anyone.

00:19:11.280 --> 00:19:13.810
But... do your feet smell that much?

00:19:13.810 --> 00:19:15.330
D-Don't question me about it!

00:19:15.330 --> 00:19:17.070
I'm embarrassed enough!

00:19:17.070 --> 00:19:18.830
I think I'm curious now, too.

00:19:20.810 --> 00:19:21.840
Hey!

00:19:22.790 --> 00:19:25.850
I ran here, so I think they
might smell a little sweaty.

00:19:26.580 --> 00:19:28.810
I can see how you'd get into it, though!

00:19:31.360 --> 00:19:33.520
You're kind of interesting.

00:19:33.930 --> 00:19:35.890
No way! I did it, Kao!

00:19:35.890 --> 00:19:38.570
She called your sister "interesting"!

00:19:39.310 --> 00:19:42.860
Hey... Would you mind talking
with me a little more?

00:19:45.630 --> 00:19:50.690
Oh... So you're going to wear
the sailor uniform from now on?

00:19:50.690 --> 00:19:52.210
That's pretty gutsy.

00:19:53.510 --> 00:19:57.120
You're Kizaki Erika-san,
and you're from T-Tokyo.

00:19:57.120 --> 00:19:58.480
Th-That's amazing!

00:19:58.480 --> 00:20:00.140
You're taking notes?

00:20:00.380 --> 00:20:02.120
You're very diligent, Akebi-san.

00:20:06.170 --> 00:20:08.900
Y-Your nail clippers are really cute.

00:20:08.900 --> 00:20:10.650
Do you carry them around all the time?

00:20:10.650 --> 00:20:12.640
No, this is the first time.

00:20:12.640 --> 00:20:16.140
In my room at home,
when I get anxious or nervous,

00:20:16.380 --> 00:20:18.650
I end up clipping my nails.

00:20:20.250 --> 00:20:23.150
This clicking sound just...

00:20:23.150 --> 00:20:25.150
relaxes me somehow.

00:20:29.030 --> 00:20:31.290
Were you anxious just now?

00:20:31.290 --> 00:20:31.970
Huh?

00:20:34.400 --> 00:20:37.920
Well... with all the firsts
I'm experiencing today,

00:20:38.210 --> 00:20:39.650
I couldn't sleep last night.

00:20:40.160 --> 00:20:43.740
I came to school early because
I couldn't just sit around any longer,

00:20:43.740 --> 00:20:45.520
but I just kept getting more nervous.

00:20:51.690 --> 00:20:53.190
Is it that funny?

00:20:53.420 --> 00:20:55.750
No, it's not that.

00:20:55.750 --> 00:20:59.850
I was just surprised someone as pretty
as you would stress like that.

00:20:59.850 --> 00:21:01.640
O-Of course I do!

00:21:01.640 --> 00:21:03.690
And my looks have nothing to do with it!

00:21:03.690 --> 00:21:05.690
Y-Yeah, you're right.

00:21:06.020 --> 00:21:08.340
I was kinda scared, though.

00:21:08.340 --> 00:21:11.470
I've never really talked to
someone my own age before.

00:21:12.190 --> 00:21:16.190
I didn't know what I'd do if I didn't
think the way everyone else does.

00:21:16.460 --> 00:21:18.280
So I'm happy!

00:21:18.280 --> 00:21:19.700
I felt the same way!

00:21:22.810 --> 00:21:25.670
Oh, I guess everyone else
will be coming in soon.

00:21:25.670 --> 00:21:28.520
I was just sitting at a random desk.

00:21:30.210 --> 00:21:31.430
Number 1...

00:21:32.220 --> 00:21:33.390
This one's mine.

00:21:34.800 --> 00:21:37.570
The closest spot to greet
everyone coming in...

00:21:37.570 --> 00:21:39.070
I'm number 5.

00:21:48.780 --> 00:21:51.780
I think I've calmed down a little.

00:21:54.780 --> 00:21:56.860
I'll be okay now.

00:22:01.990 --> 00:22:04.040
Maybe I can do this, too.

00:22:06.870 --> 00:22:08.090
Good morning!
